en-US.title: Identity Hormones & Healthcare
en-US.description: Identity Hormones & Healthcare is a specialty healthcare provider for the LGBTQI+ community and its allies. The clinic offers a wide range of services including Gender Affirming Hormone Therapy, HIV and PrEP care, and Testosterone Replacement treatments. Healthcare at Identity Hormones & Healthcare is personalized, with treatments tailored to meet the specific needs of each individual. The clinic also offers telemedicine services for the convenience of patients.

address: 100 E Camelback Rd #108, Phoenix, AZ 85012, USA
